title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 18 §§ 398-9.1 - Checks
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 18 §§ 398-9.1 - Checks

State Regulations
A reported lost or stolen check for State benefits that
has been confirmed as uncashed and has not been sent to unclaimed funds will be
replaced by SSP benefits or SSPNA. Notes
